metadata.name: Goodaz (Official Music Video) by Evaflow
metadata.description:
'Goodaz' is a term commonly used in Jamaica to refer to someone who you find attractive, especially physically. However, I thought a woman being a 'Goodaz' should have more to do with her spiritual and mental features rather than her physical features: a woman who is self-aware, keen on spirituality and also focused on success in the material world.  This song was the result.

You rock the worl’ when you do dat
